'''''Popular Automaton''''' was a successful [[Holomag/Legends|holomag]] that reviewed [[Droid/Legends|droid]] models. It had an annual ranking of the droid industry, decided by subscribers' votes; in one such article, [[TT-8L gatekeeper droid/Legends|TT-8L]] droids were named the "Most Annoying" models on the market.

